      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I'm a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been babied since day one, kept in a garage, and it\u2019s totally spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one. Come take it for a spin, you\u2019re going to love it!",
