    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system for razor-sharp throttle response. This example is mechanically flawless, with documented rod bearing replacement and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. Power is routed through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory variable M-differential. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, complemented by a pristine interior and original paint with zero oxidation. Every bushing, seal, and heat shield is in showroom condition, making this a definitive example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
