    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a true showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior is finished in a deep, mirror-like gloss, entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every panel gap is factory-perfect, and the trim remains dark and supple. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of creasing or bolster wear, and it retains that distinct factory-fresh scent. All technological features, including the high-fidelity sound system and navigation, operate with precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. This vehicle drives with the same tightness and responsiveness it possessed on day one. For the discerning buyer seeking a collector-grade example without compromise, this car stands in a class of its own.",
